          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1087,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022\",\"id\":\"msg_01WDnMAf3g4bJEHVByqyVMyu\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Space Exploration Landing Page\\n\\nYour vision evokes the awe-inspiring journey of humanity reaching for the stars, reminiscent of NASA's elegant design language and SpaceX's modern aesthetic, with a touch of sci-fi wonder from films like Interstellar.\\n\\n## Key Features\\n- **Hero Section**: Dynamic animation of planets and spacecraft\\n- **Mission Timeline**: Interactive history of space exploration\\n- **Latest Discoveries**: Real-time updates from current space missions\\n- **Interactive Galaxy Map**: Explorable visualization of our cosmic neighborhood\\n- **Newsletter**: Space exploration updates and launch notifications\\n\\nWait a moment while I build your landing page.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":302,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":139,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
